    {
      "title": "<span id=\"#27961\" class=\"scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold flex items-center\"><h1 class=\"inline !mb-1 scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold\">characterise</h1><div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(v.)</div></span>",
      "html": "<p>这是“<a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of characterize \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/characterize\">characterize</a>”的主要英式拼写方式； 有关后缀，请参见 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of -ize \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/-ize\">-ize</a>。相关词形包括： <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">Characterised</i> 和 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">characterising</i>。</p>"
